#, c-format
msgid ""
"Frequency plots are not available with excitation type %d.\n"
"This model uses Incident Field or Elementary Current Source excitation.\n"
"Change the EX card to type 0 (Applied E Field) or 5 (Current Discontinuity)."
msgstr ""
"Frekvenču grafiki nav pieejami ar ierosmes tipu %d.\n"
"Šis modelis izmanto Krītošā lauka vai Elementārā strāvas avota ierosmi.\n"
"Mainiet EX karti uz tipu 0 (Pieliktais E lauks) vai 5 (Strāvas pārrāvums)."

